 â„ï¸ 6. Amazon S3 Glacier (Complete Overview)

 âœ… Definition

S3 Glacier ek low-cost archival storage hai jo:

 Long-term data ke liye use hota hai
 Rarely accessed data store karta hai

---

 ðŸ§± Glacier Concepts (Old Naming â€“ Understanding)

 Vault = Bucket
 Archive = Object

---

 ðŸ“¦ Glacier Storage Limits

 Archive size: very large (TBs me)
 Designed for massive data storage

---

 ðŸ” Glacier Access

 Instant nahi hota (except Glacier Instant Retrieval)
 Minutes to hours lag sakte hain

---

 ðŸŽ¯ Use Case

 Legal records
 Audit logs
 Old backups
 Compliance data

